    "body" : "<p>Just use <code>withDayOfMonth</code>, and <code>lengthOfMonth()</code>:</p>\n<pre><code>LocalDate initial = LocalDate.of(2014, 2, 13);\nLocalDate start = initial.withDayOfMonth(1);\nLocalDate end = initial.withDayOfMonth(initial.getMonth().length(initial.isLeapYear()));\n</code></pre>\n"
