    "body" : "<p>If anyone comes looking for <strong>first day of previous month</strong> and <strong>last day of previous month</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>public static LocalDate firstDayOfPreviousMonth(LocalDate date) {\n        return date.minusMonths(1).withDayOfMonth(1);\n    }\n\n\npublic static LocalDate lastDayOfPreviousMonth(LocalDate date) {\n        return date.withDayOfMonth(1).minusDays(1);\n    }\n</code></pre>\n\n\n"
  }, {
